title: Global Day of Coderetreat 2015 - Vienna, Austria
description:
For the third time in a row, FREQUENTIS will host the GDCR in Vienna, Austria! 
To register for this event, get a ticket on Eventbrite on this page (https://www.eventbrite.com/e/global-day-of-coderetreat-2015-vienna-austria-tickets-18982996654).
